    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Byrrhinae: Pseudomorychus spp.: A – C: P. mixtus (Lea): A, habitus, dorsal, Length = 2.3 mm; B, habitus, lateral; C. pterothorax, ventral, with left mesocoxa removed. D – E, P. torrensensis (Blackburn): D, fore leg; E, habitus, dorsal, length = 3.2 mm." ;
